Architecture: all
Description: MultiFlexi HTML documentation
 Sphinx-generated HTML documentation for MultiFlexi, a PHP-based task
 scheduling and automation framework for accounting system integrations.
 .
 An Apache2 configuration snippet is enabled automatically on installation.
 An Nginx configuration snippet is installed to /usr/share/doc/multiflexi/.
